---
---

<section class="py-24 lg:py-32 bg-[#F5F0E6] relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Subtle grid pattern -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.02]" style="background-image: linear-gradient(#D4A853 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, #D4A853 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 60px 60px;"></div>

  <!-- Ambient warm glow -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[800px] h-[800px] bg-[#D4A853]/8 rounded-full blur-[200px]"></div>

  <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-24 items-center">
      <!-- Text Content -->
      <div class="space-y-8 reveal">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="w-12 h-[2px] bg-[#D4A853]"></div>
          <span class="text-[#B8923E] text-sm font-medium tracking-[0.3em] uppercase font-['Space_Grotesk']">About Us</span>
        </div>

        <h2 class="font-['Space_Grotesk'] text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-[#1A1A2E] leading-[1.1] tracking-tight">
          Architects of
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#D4A853] via-[#C9993D] to-[#B8923E] bg-clip-text text-transparent"> Ambition</span>
        </h2>

        <p class="text-[#1A1A2E]/70 text-lg lg:text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
          That's who we are. Welcome to Punjab Angels, India's foremost platform dedicated to cultivating an startup ecosystem. We are more than just an investment network; we are architects of ambition, fostering a community where passionate founders thrive.
        </p>

        <p class="text-[#1A1A2E]/50 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
          At Punjab Angels, we're not just building businesses; we're building a future. We take pride in nurturing visionary founders, equipping them with a profound understanding of venture investing as a powerful asset class. Our commitment extends beyond funding; we're here to create platforms where both founders and investors embark on a journey of learning, investing, and unparalleled growth. We don't just invest in businesses; we invest in the limitless potential of dreams.
        </p>

        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="group inline-flex items-center gap-3 text-[#B8923E] font-semibold hover:text-[#D4A853] transition-colors duration-300"
        >
          <span>Talk With Us</span>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-300" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Visual Block -->
      <div class="reveal" style="animation-delay: 200ms;">
        <div class="relative">
          <!-- Main decorative block -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 lg:p-10 shadow-lg border border-[#D4A853]/10">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-5">
              <div class="text-center p-5 bg-[#F5F0E6] rounded-2xl border border-[#D4A853]/10">
                <span class="font-['Space_Grotesk'] text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-[#D4A853] to-[#B8923E] bg-clip-text text-transparent">50+</span>
                <p class="text-[#1A1A2E]/60 mt-2 text-sm">Startups Funded</p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center p-5 bg-[#F5F0E6] rounded-2xl border border-[#D4A853]/10">
                <span class="font-['Space_Grotesk'] text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-[#D4A853] to-[#B8923E] bg-clip-text text-transparent">100+</span>
                <p class="text-[#1A1A2E]/60 mt-2 text-sm">Investors</p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center p-5 bg-[#F5F0E6] rounded-2xl border border-[#D4A853]/10">
                <span class="font-['Space_Grotesk'] text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-[#D4A853] to-[#B8923E] bg-clip-text text-transparent">12+</span>
                <p class="text-[#1A1A2E]/60 mt-2 text-sm">Partners</p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center p-5 bg-[#F5F0E6] rounded-2xl border border-[#D4A853]/10">
                <span class="font-['Space_Grotesk'] text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-[#D4A853] to-[#B8923E] bg-clip-text text-transparent">20+</span>
                <p class="text-[#1A1A2E]/60 mt-2 text-sm">Events Yearly</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Decorative elements -->
          <div class="absolute -top-6 -right-6 w-32 h-32 bg-[#D4A853]/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-8 -left-8 w-40 h-40 bg-[#D4A853]/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
          <!-- Corner accent -->
          <div class="absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-4 h-4 border-t-2 border-r-2 border-[#D4A853]/40 rounded-tr-lg"></div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-2 -left-2 w-4 h-4 border-b-2 border-l-2 border-[#D4A853]/40 rounded-bl-lg"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
